## ✨ The "Magic Number" (Block Size) Shortcut

**Magic number = 256 − (mask value of the last non-255 octet).** Subnets increment by this number.

| Mask (last octet) | CIDR | Magic Number |
|---|---|---|
| 128 | /25 | 128 |
| 192 | /26 | 64 |
| 224 | /27 | 32 |
| 240 | /28 | 16 |

